    <item>
      <title>无论谁获胜，英国债务问题都将牵动下届政府的命运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/uk-debt-hangover-ties-next-government-s-hands-whoever-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无论哪个政党在7月4日赢得英国大选，巨大的债务危机都将接踵而至，这将严重限制在民意调查中领先的工党或执政的保守党在执政期间的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/uk-debt-hangover-ties-next-government-s-hands-whoever-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国防部长在首次全球论坛上猛烈批评美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/china-defense-chief-swipes-at-us-at-his-first-global-forum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国防部长董军在就任新职务后首次出席全球安全论坛，尖锐批评美国在台湾问题上“掏空”北京的一个中国政策以及在南海问题上“误导”一个国家，并采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/china-defense-chief-swipes-at-us-at-his-first-global-forum</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 02:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>祖马再次强调南非选举结果存在差异</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/zuma-doubles-down-on-allegation-of-south-africa-vote-discrepancy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非前总统雅各布·祖马再次指控选票统计存在差异，尽管选举结果显示，他新成立的“人民之矛”党已经蚕食了执政党非洲人国民大会的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/zuma-doubles-down-on-allegation-of-south-africa-vote-discrepancy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>出口民调显示莫迪有望在印度大选中赢得压倒性胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/initial-india-exit-polls-show-modi-s-party-set-for-majority-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多项出口民意调查显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党将连续第三次在印度大选中赢得决定性多数，从而延续其十年执政，领导这个全球增长最快的主要经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/initial-india-exit-polls-show-modi-s-party-set-for-majority-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 13:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非非国大准备迎接竞争对手谈判，因为多数席位已崩盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-african-election-a-historic-rebuke-for-the-anc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非执政党在失去维持 30 年的议会多数席位后，正准备与激烈的竞争对手就新政府的组成展开艰苦的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/south-african-election-a-historic-rebuke-for-the-anc</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 06:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
